<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16428</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天很热。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16428</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25056</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比流着汗，走向儿童中心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31658</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜和莉琪用纸扇子互相扇风。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36066</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天我们做什么？” 波比问雪莉老师，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36066</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以去室外吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39707</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45858</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天这么热，我正要带你们出去。” 雪莉老师笑着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拿一个水瓶，跟我走吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们跟着雪莉老师来到足球场。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60591</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天我们要玩儿水枪抓人游戏。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66179</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“水枪抓人游戏？” 莉琪说，“那是什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70296</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一个人负责抓。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70296</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77742</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“抓的人必须抓到其他所有人。 抓人需要把水喷到这个人身上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77742</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果你被喷到了，就被‘冻住了’ ，不能动！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90591</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有人都被抓到以后，我们再决定谁来抓人。” 雪莉老师看着大家，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92658</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“明白了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95012</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95012</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98092</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁先抓呢？” 伊坦问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98092</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100972</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100972</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在想一个1到20之间的数字。” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105962</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108733</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“猜猜是什么数字。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“11！” 波比大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115175</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“6。” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115175</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117880</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“15。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117880</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120664</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“19。” 伊坦说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120664</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“10。” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129559</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是11。” 雪莉老师说，“波比，你来抓！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129559</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“耶！” 波比欢呼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135891</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家把水瓶放下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135891</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141658</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们先站成一个圆圈。波比，你站在中间。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147962</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师站在圆圈外面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147962</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“各就各位，预备，开始！” 雪莉老师吹了吹哨子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比去追伊坦。但是，伊坦太快了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159437</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162542</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比决定等会儿再来抓他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162542</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他转身，看到尼娜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166844</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173300</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他快速跑向尼娜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173300</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178447</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！” 尼娜被水喷到后，尖叫了一声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178447</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183525</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你要冻住！” 莉琪刚好跑过，提醒她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186554</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在波比在追莉琪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191624</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拿起水瓶……嗞！莉琪被冻住了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>水从她的额头流下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197193</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比追着贾森。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200330</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森看上去又热又累。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里有水让你凉一凉！” 波比大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204577</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把水喷到贾森背后。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈！水真凉！” 贾森笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211032</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他被冻住了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你一定抓不到我！” 伊坦大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217655</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跑过足球场。波比在后面追着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223697</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦跑来跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227840</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比靠近过一次，但伊坦躲开了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235113</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239876</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！” 波比突然能量爆发。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239876</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他以最快的速度奔跑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244662</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦的脚拌了一下！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252213</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗞！水从伊坦的背后流下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252213</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们都被冻住了！” 波比开心地喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257151</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“游戏结束！” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比很热，气喘吁吁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267884</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真好玩儿！” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267884</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272529</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们再来一次吧！” 伊坦看着雪莉老师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好。” 雪莉老师说，“波比，你来决定谁抓人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286439</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好。我在想一个1到20之间的数字。” 波比说完笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286439</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>平时他不喜欢在抓人游戏里被抓。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，现在被水喷到一定很凉快！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>